entries.title: The iPhone 15 Wi-Fi 6E upgrade might just be for the Pro models
entries.description: The standard iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Plus phones look set to stick with Wi-Fi 6 when they arrive later this year.

entries.title: Another flurry of Samsung Galaxy S23 price leaks have turned up
entries.description: It looks as though the Galaxy S23 will cost more than the Galaxy S22 in most parts of the world.
